            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1596545813717-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>paprika</strong> <strong>chicken breasts</strong> in half so that you are left with 4 <span class=\"text-danger\">[8] </span>pieces</p><p>Deseed the<strong> pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into quarters</p><p>Drain the <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>drained mozzarella</strong> into 4 <span class=\"text-danger\">[8] </span>pieces</p>",
      "order": 3,
