        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Layer the <strong>paprika chicken </strong>followed by a<strong> pepper quarter</strong> (hollow of the pepper facing up) then the <strong>torn</strong> <strong>mozzarella</strong></p><p>Repeat this again and insert a <strong>skewer</strong> down the centre so that everything stays in place – these are your <strong>smoky chicken stacks</strong></p>",
