      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>remaining smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>remaining cider vinegar </strong>in a small bowl</p><p>Season with a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> smoky mayo</strong></p>",
